1) Create Stack > Template is Ready > Upload a template file
	Choose File (Which we downloaded in system)
	Next
	Stack Name (EC2-Stack)
	Parameters InstanceType (t3.small) > KeyName (Select an existing key) > Next > Next > Submit
	
2) Check EC2 > for the instance which need be created by CloudFormation
3) we can chenge or Update the instance as below
	Go to CloudFormation > Update Stack > InstanceType (t2.micro) > Submit
4) Now go to EC2 there instance will be updated with the new instance type as t2.micro
